# Dev Script Awareness Rule

- Before suggesting manual command sequences, check `scripts/` for existing helpers.
- Prefer using and updating `scripts/dev_api_local.sh`, `scripts/dev_frontend.sh`, `scripts/dev_api_docker.sh`, and `scripts/dev_frontend_docker.sh`.
- Keep both workflows supported when possible: hybrid (`backend in Docker + frontend local`) and full Docker.
- When behavior changes, update script-related docs in `README.md` and `front-end/README.md` in the same increment.
- Keep scripts non-interactive and safe for repeated runs.
